column5: Brian...You are eager aren't you.  I was considering buying a new Chrysler but think I am going to wait until the fall to make a decision on a vehicle.  Want to make sure that the businesses are around.  Great deals to be had right now though.  I wish I knew I was having another kid when I bought my accord in August!

Steve, I dont see much happening for awhile.Myself, I will be looking at a new truck this June.Dirt cheap from what I have been hearing ,and the gas will always be up and down.  So hows the work outs going bud?  Been swimming all week.Great workout.Up at 5 am and swim from 6 til 7.
I have had a pretty good week, Brian.  I was travelling this week so it was harder to watch the food.  Tomorow should be a good one.  I will start swimming soon.
Told a long time ago, If I wanted your opinion I would give it too you.  ~Quote dad.
You 2 guys into that fancy Syncronized swimming thing?
I might be able to get a picture of a dock covered with smallies that should get er locked up.
Is it my imagination or have there been a lot of locked threads as of late? Jim
Less than most springs Jim!
Just the time of year. Normal stuff. We have extra staff on hand for it...lol.
but none are my fault   I'm slipping
Even better... the threads that just... disappear
Yes Terry your slipping bud
How can we get this one locked? I've got a few ideas but I better not!
theres at least one more lock up brewing as we speak
Jim, I can't believe you're holding that poor Bass vertically in your avatar pic!!! You obviously have no regard for the poor thing!!!
but just look at AILE GOBY as he has been lit on fire!
Ha......just wait until next week!!!
I say it's aboot time the mods did a little work and earnened the big bux they make!!!        ... time to get off yer   -es and lock this one down boyz!!!

I find it really funny when the original poster has something along the lines of "in my opinion, anyway" right in the sub-heading of the thread...but people still feel the need to jump all over and personally attack the guy, as though he doesn't have the right to a different opinion.
The way things are going pretty soon you will be allowed a opinion.
Sorry guys, we're doing the best we can.
when certain posters make assumptions that all fish in pictures are slaughtered ... people react
(is this week a record?)   Not yet.....
Great to hear... a wonderful improvement over my days as a child when I WASN'T allowed an opinion Bob ! lol
Steve is right dude. There is a time when you have to look within and say "did I screw up?" and when you are outnumbered a bajillion to one, the answer is usually "YES". Jim
LOL..... it was suppose to read NOT allowed but my fingers don't go as fast as my mind. As a matter of fact my mind has been GONE for a long time..
I guess if we would all behave ourselves....
Tiller  DANG...BEER...WINGS...ELITISM
Now Steve,stay off them darn wings bud.Hope thats light beer BTW. LOL   I was going to start a CAW/CRYSLER POST,BUT GUESS FOLKS CARE MORE FOR THE BIG BUCKS AND NOT THIER JOBS FOR A LIFE.
